								<div class="flex items-start">
									<div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
										<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
											<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
										</svg>
									</div>
									<div>
										<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Segundo cuatrimestre</h4>
										<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Martes y jueves de 10:00 a 12:00</p>
